---
title: "US57 — Review expert applications"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsApprovalScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>ReviewExpertVerification
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertVerificationDocument · ExpertProfile
  A->>B: open pending application + documents
  B->>C: review(expertId)
  C->>E: inspect documents
  alt approve
    C->>E: verification_status → verified, role → expert
    B-->>A: expert goes live
  else reject
    C->>E: verification_status → rejected (+reason)
    B-->>A: applicant notified
  end
  note over E: persisted via SupabaseGateway
